food down here is going to be bad?

744
00:56:44,490 --> 00:56:45,896
Okay, bye.

745
00:56:46,632 --> 00:56:49,691
Okay, guys,
listen up. You are going to swim.

746
00:56:49,693 --> 00:56:52,463
