793
00:59:32,053 --> 00:59:34,020
- Mohammed! Mohammed!
- What?

794
00:59:34,022 --> 00:59:35,989
Come! Let's go! Come, come!

795
00:59:35,991 --> 00:59:39,102
- What?
- Let's go!

796
00:59:40,666 --> 00:59:42,765
Oh! Whoo!

797
00:59:44,406 --> 00:59:45,999
Wonderful!

798
00:59:49,747 --> 00:59:52,083
- Some champagne.
- Bravo!

