862
01:04:14,137 --> 01:04:16,005
Sir.

863
01:04:20,275 --> 01:04:21,714
So, good evening.

864
01:04:21,716 --> 01:04:24,013
For tonight's first meal,
we will be serving you

865
01:04:24,015 --> 01:04:27,181
