- Yes, we did, darling.

887
01:05:59,913 --> 01:06:02,585
And we still love each other.

888
01:06:02,587 --> 01:06:04,488
- A toast!
- Oh, yeah.

889
01:06:05,281 --> 01:06:08,381
Er... to love!

890
01:06:09,693 --> 01:06:11,054
- To love.
- To love.

891
01:06:20,605 --> 01:06:22,868
- Sir.
- Madam.

