yuzu vinaigrette.

895
01:06:38,050 --> 01:06:39,918
- Enjoy!
- Thank you.

896
01:06:43,484 --> 01:06:46,023
- Hmm!
- Hmm...

897
01:06:53,164 --> 01:06:56,363
- Are you enjoying yourself?
- Yes.

898
01:06:56,365 --> 01:06:58,332
Madam.

899
01:07:18,992 --> 01:07:20,564
Sir.

