01:08:24,762 --> 01:08:26,861
Are you okay?

911
01:08:33,429 --> 01:08:36,268
Madam? Dagueneau,
French, Sauvignon blanc?

912
01:08:36,377 --> 01:08:37,448
<i>Champignon...</i>

913
01:08:37,487 --> 01:08:38,781
